Quote:  I slipped on the bloodied floor and the carcase should have fallen on me, but the wheel jammed somehow on the rail and I crouched under swinging death, sick in the guts. The board-walker had to climb up on the wall and saw through the hind leg.  <i>IBid.</i> 67 The boardwalker came in for men to help with the cleaning up and I said you can stuff that, sport.
